'''Tsukinami-no-matsuri''' is a [[Matsuri|Japanese festival]] done at {{ill|Isonokami Shrine|en}}.

It is celebrated on fixed days of the month, for example the 1st and 15th.<ref>{{Cite web|date=2023-03-22|title=Tsukinami no matsuri {{!}} 國學院大學デジタルミュージアム|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230322103159/https://d-museum.kokugakuin.ac.jp/bts/detail/?id=4026|access-date=2024-04-26|website=web.archive.org}}</ref>

